      <para id="import-auto-idm984927824"> The result shows that the overflow is dependent on the sign bits of the two numbers, and the result. An overflow occurs when summing two positive numbers but the result is negative, or summing two negative numbers but the result is positive. The Boolean expression for the overflow is as follows:</para>
