    <section id="import-auto-idm1238884192">
      <title>Real Numbers</title>
      <para id="import-auto-idm1213860032">A decimal real number is composed of the integral part and the fraction part. Conversion of a decimal number to or from other representations can be performed on the integral part and the fraction part individually. The integral part will be converted using techniques described in other sections.  In this section, we will focus on the fraction part conversion.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm1039356752">According to the definition, <m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mi>…</m:mi><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msub><m:mi>.</m:mi><m:msub><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mi>…</m:mi><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:munderover><m:mo stretchy="false">∑</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mi>i</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:munderover><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>i</m:mi></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mi>×</m:mi><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mi>i</m:mi></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">+</m:mo><m:mrow><m:munderover><m:mo stretchy="false">∑</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mi>j</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:munderover><m:msub><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mi>j</m:mi></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mi>×</m:mi><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:mi>j</m:mi></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0">{a} rsub {n-1} {a} rsub {n-2} {a} rsub {n-3} … {a} rsub {2} {a} rsub {1} {a} rsub {0} . {b} rsub {0} {b} rsub {1} {…b} rsub {m-1} {b} rsub {m} = sum from {i=0} to {n-1} {{a} rsub {i}} × {r} ^ {i} + sum from {j=0} to {m} {{b} rsub {j}} × {10} ^ {-j}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math